of hsbc financial corp ltd and has been its director since september  he has been director of security capital group inc since  he serves as a director of cs tech inc and pharmaceutical industries llc he serves as a life trustee of rush university rush university medical center and the brookings institution he serves as a trustee of the institutional boards including the american china forum chicago council on foreign relations of which he is former chairman the commercial club of chicago chicago symphony orchestra garvin school of international management of which he is former chairman and big shoulders fund for parochial schools he served as director of microage inc since january   and allegheny energy supply company llc since  he served as nonemployee director of virgin america inc from  to december   he served as a director of sitel corporation since october  and chiquita brands international inc from march  to may   mr freidheim served as independent director of allegheny energy inc from october   to february   and served as its presiding director from may   to february   mr freidheim served as lead director and director of hsbc finance corp formerly household international inc since  he served as an independent director of suntimes media group inc from  to january   mr freidheim is a member of the advisory council of the mendosa school of business at the university of notre dame mr freidheim holds a bs in chemical engineering from the university of notre dame an ms in industrial administration from carnegie mellon university a phd honorary in international law from thunderbird the garvin school of international management and an mba from carnegie mellon universityread full background corporate headquarters  north orleans streetchicago illinois united statesphone fax  board members memberships trusteethe brookings institutiontrusteerush universitypresentdirectorsecurity capital group incorporatedpresentlead directorhsbc financial corporation limited education m