cation group prior to his role at investcorp freidheim was executive vice president president kenmore craftsman  diehard for sears holdings and cao and executive vice president of lehman brothers holdings inc freidheim began his career in investment banking in chicago at john nuveen  co in  he joined lehman brothers’ investment banking division in  he took the position of vp office of the chairman for lehman brothers’ ceo richard s fuld jr since then he held a number officer positions in each of the investment management investment banking and corporate divisions freidheim was appointed cocao in october  nonprofit involvementedit in  scott freidheim was named a young global leader by the world economic forum as a leader in the field of business since  freidheim has participated in many panels at the world economic forum in davos switzerland as well as at the inaugural new champions meeting in dalian china and was a member of the wefs global agenda council scott freidheim is a member of the board of trustees of the institute of international education iie which administers the fulbright scholarship program as well as the board and selection committee of the iies scholar rescue fund he is a former member of the board of trustees of spelman college freidheim is a member of the economic club of new york and the council on foreign relations and of the chatham house educationedit freidheim attended northwestern university and holds a ba in economics from northwestern university and an mba from the kellogg school of management freidheim was a division  athlete playing soccer while attending northwestern university involvement with northwesternedit freidheim is a benefactor of northwestern university he is actively involved with the school and has a soccer scholarship in his name family and personal lifeedit freidheim was born in dearborn michigan and was raised in brazil and france as a child while his father opened offices abroad for booz allen hamilton his father also served as ceo of chiquita brands international and of the chicago suntimes his brother stephen freidheim is a hedge fund manager who founder of cyrus capital in new york and cofounded virgin america with richard branson freidheim is married to isabelle dufour freidheim who is a venture capitalist referencesedit  httpinvestingbusinessweekcomresearchstocksprivatepersonasppersonidprivcapidpreviouscapidprevioustitlevirginamericainc  httpwwwforbescomprofilecyrusffreidheimjr  httparticlesphillycombusinessscottfreidheimcdicorpwaltergarrison  httpwwwprnewswirecomnewsreleasescdicorpboardofdirectorsacceptsresignationofscottfreidheimceohtml  httpinvestingbusinessweekcomresearchstocksprivatesnapshotaspprivcapid  isabelle dufour freidheim   vanity fair lehman’s desperate housewives by vicky ward april  external linksedit httponlinewsjcomarticlebtcohtml httpwwwftcomcmssaefccaedcabhtmlnclickcheck httpwwwforbescomfinancemktguideappspersoninfofrompersonidpersontearsheetjhtmlpassedpersonid httpsearchftcomsearchsortbygadatearticlequerytextdavidgoldfarb httpinvestingbusinessweekcomresearchstockspeoplepersonasppersonidsymbollehmqpk httpwwwspelmaneduadministrationofficetrusteesnotesshtml retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlescottjfreidheimoldid categories american chief executives birthsliving peoplenorthwestern university alumnikellogg school of management alumnilehman brothers peoplewef ygl honoreeschatham househidden categories pages using infobox person with unknown parametersinfobox person using religionpages to import images to wikidataarticles with hcards navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informat